issue.title: Unknown format "lastNameFemaleMarried"
issue.body:
### Summary

I get the following exception if I use the `$faker->name` property/method.

### Versions

|                | Version |
|:---------------|:--------|
| PHP            | 7.3   |
| `fakerphp/faker`  | 1.20.0   |

### Self-enclosed code snippet for reproduction

```php
\Faker\Factory::create('hu_HU')->name
```

### Expected output

```txt
a random hungarian name
```

### Actual output

```txt
[InvalidArgumentException] Unknown format "lastNameFemaleMarried"  
```

comment.body: Yes it is fixed in main, but a stable release would be great.

release.body: update readme.md with correct package and repository names
release.short_description_html: update readme.md with correct package and repository names

commits.message:
update package name and urls in readme.md

because it is not restricted to Yii 2.0 anymore

release.body: Since this release it is possible to use CodeSniffer from v3.7.1.
release.short_description_html: Since this release it is possible to use CodeSniffer from v3.7.1.

commits.message: use github actions instead of travis
add custom, psr-12 based ruleset to other files and fix ident style
add extended psr-12 ruleset and fix ident style
fix to configure custom OperatorSpacing sniff
do not validate native codeception method in Cest files
remove rules that can find in PSR-12 or not necessary
remove condition formatting rule that is defined in PSR-12
